🆕 **v0.3.0** • 01 Juli 2026

**🎨 Visual & Branding:**
• 🖼️ Logo resmi NovaPlay SAMP terpasang
• 📱 App icon launcher — logo NovaPlay SAMP (bukan Flutter default lagi)
• ✨ Splash screen animasi fade-in + scale + loading bar cyan
• 🏠 Logo tampil di header Home screen
• 🌑 Background splash dark navy + glow effect

**⚡ Fitur:**
• 📡 Live ping realtime via UDP SA-MP protocol
• 🏷️ Hostname server otomatis (nama server asli, bukan IP)
• 👥 Player count realtime
• 🟢 Status Online/Offline otomatis
• 🎯 Ping color-coded: hijau/kuning/merah
• 🖥️ Server info card di Home (Players, Ping, Password)
• 🔘 Empty card "No server selected" → tap ke server list

**🔧 Perbaikan:**
• Fix background logo header (ClipRRect)
• App name di launcher: "NovaPlay SAMP"
• INTERNET permission otomatis saat build
• Build workflow makin stabil

**🚧 Coming soon:**
